This is the AmigaGuide® file EqEd.guide, produced by Makeinfo-1.55 from 
the input file eqed.texi.

   This file documents Equation Edit, a program to edit equations in a
WYSIWYG manner.

   Copyright 1994-1996 Brian Aagaard Petersen


@Node Main "EqEd.guide"
@Next "Introduction"

Equation Edit
*************

   Equation Edit (EqEd) is a program to create mathematical equations
and expressions, which is to be inserted in a report or similar. It
supports output to LaTeX and wordprocessors.

   This is for version 0.97 Beta release


 @{" Introduction " Link "Introduction"}       - What is this thing
 @{" Requirements " Link "Requirements"}       - Will it run on my system?
